Plot: Bheeman realizes the inconvenience caused by an old pathway when he had to take his mother to the hospital. His life takes an interesting turn when he decides to broaden the pathway.

Name: Bachelor
Plot: A deeply flawed guy with behavioral issues and conservative background get into a live-in relationship with a hep modern girl and the problems that follow

Name: Mission Extreme
Plot: After bringing down the man behind the Dhaka Attack, head of bomb disposal unit Abid Rahman learns that an invisible threat hovers over Bangladesh.

Name: Last Looks
Plot: A disgraced ex-cop seeks solace by moving to the woods, but his quiet life comes to an end when a private eye recruits him to investigate a murder.

Name: Being the Ricardos
Plot: Follows Lucy and Desi as they face a crisis that could end their careers--and another that could end their marriage.

Name: Single All the Way
Plot: Desperate to avoid his family's judgment about his perpetual single status, Peter convinces his best friend Nick to join him for the holidays and pretend that they're now in a relationship.

Name: The Whole Truth
Plot: When two siblings stumble on a strange hole in the wall of their grandparents' house, horrifying incidents reveal sinister secrets about their family.

Name: Tadap
Plot: Unforeseen circumstances threaten the passionate relationship between star-crossed lovers.

Name: Akhanda
Plot: When the nefarious Varadarajulu plans to attack Murali Krishna, an ardent devotee of Lord Shiva, Akhanda leaves no stone unturned to defeat the evil.

Name: Nightmare Alley
Plot: A grifter working his way up from low-ranking carnival worker to lauded psychic medium matches wits with a psychologist bent on exposing him.

Name: The Pilot: A Battle for Survival
Plot: During a mission in WWII, the plane of Nikolai Komlev is shot down. He manages to bring his plane down in a remote forest clearing, but far from friendly territory, he faces a relentless test of physical and mental endurance.

Name: Zoey's Extraordinary Christmas
Plot: On her first holiday without her father, Zoey wants to create a magical Christmas for her family just like the ones Mitch used to do.

Name: The Perfect Family
Plot: Lucia's achievement of a perfect family is threatened by her son's loose living, dirty mouthed girlfriend and possible in laws that are not what she pictured for him.

Name: Mistletoe Mixup
Plot: A workaholic with no time for romance, or the holidays, meets two potential suitors on the same day, who turn out to be brothers. A sibling squabble commences in this holiday romance.

Name: Marakkar: Lion of the Arabian Sea
Plot: Set in the 16th century, the story of Kunjali Marakkar IV, the naval chieftain of the Zamorin of Calicut, and his organization of India's first-ever naval defense against European forces.

Name: Breaking Up in Rome
Plot: A romantic comedy about how hard it is to separate after many years of living together.

Name: West Side Story
Plot: An adaptation of the 1957 musical, West Side Story explores forbidden love and the rivalry between the Jets and the Sharks, two teenage street gangs of different ethnic backgrounds.

Name: 14 Peaks: Nothing Is Impossible
Plot: Fearless Nepali mountaineer Nirmal Purja embarks on a seemingly impossible quest to summit all 14 of the world's 8,000-meter peaks in seven months.

Name: Rose Blood: A Friday the 13th Fan Film
Plot: Takes place 13 months after Friday The 13th Part VII. We follow Tina Shepard as she is held and studied at the infamous Camp Crystal Lake Research Facility. Tina realizes that she is not alone. There in fact is another New Blood. Rose.

Name: Werewolf Castle
Plot: Village boy Thorfinn accompanies a group of Knights on a dangerous quest to end a werewolf invasion.

Name: Katips
Plot: A tale of the young, in their fight for their ideals, how big can one get against a force too much bigger than yourself?

Name: The Wait
Plot: Updated version of a 19th century romance set on an island in the Finland archipelago sea.

Name: Girls to Buy
Plot: It follows a young woman who becomes an escort as a way of getting out of her small town, but she soon discovers she has no control over her situation.

Name: A Castle for Christmas
Plot: To escape a scandal, a bestselling author journeys to Scotland, where she falls in love with a castle - and faces off with the grumpy duke who owns it.

Name: Not to Forget
Plot: After a lifetime of scams, a self-centered millennial is sentenced to take care of his grandmother, who has Alzheimer's. This film aims to raise awareness and funds to end Alzheimer's, and is part of the project Let's Make a Difference.

Name: Govinda Govinda
Plot: Govinda Govinda involves the lives of two crime gangs, college back-benchers, wannabe film-maker and an actress, whose lives get entangled in ways no one can imagine.
Vikram Rathod(Dr. Mohan) is a sincere police officer who is transferred to the Nizampeta village to control the atrocities that are happening there.

Name: Satyameva Jayate 2
Plot: Satyameva Jayate 2 revolves around the fight against injustice and misuse of power. From police and politicians to industrialists and a common man, the film will explore corruption in all spheres.

Name: The Ambush
Plot: When three Emirati soldiers are ambushed in a hostile territory, their commander leads a daring mission to rescue them.

Name: Antim: The Final Truth
Plot: The cop played by Salman fights the land mafia in the film.

Name: The Generation of Evil
Plot: Commissioner Gintas must undertake the investigation of a series of heinous murders, a dangerous task that could expose the many dirty secrets of several prominent members of the social elite of a small Lithuanian town.
